collectors: D.D. Andrew
notes: Bottom of gully between two moderate slopes. Grey brown silty clay on metasediment. Eucalyptus viminalis, E. pauciflora grassy woodland with Chrysocephalum apiculatum, Lissanthe strigosa, Rubus fruticosus, Poa sieberiana. Tree to c. 15.0m. Brown grey ribbony bark to c. 4.0m, grey white smooth gum bark above. DBH c. 0.95m.  Buds 3-7s.
